00:16:16,508 --> 00:16:18,148
It was also her who wrote
the anonymous letter

294
00:16:18,467 --> 00:16:19,308
to the research institute.

295
00:16:20,548 --> 00:16:21,508
Even though it was supposed
to be anonymous,

296
00:16:21,508 --> 00:16:23,068
most people already knew

297
00:16:23,107 --> 00:16:23,827
who wrote it.

298
00:16:24,308 --> 00:16:25,188
Because last year,

299
00:16:25,227 --> 00:16:28,028
his wife went to Li Shu's institute

300
00:16:28,028 --> 00:16:28,827
and made a scene there.

301
00:16:30,388 --> 00:16:31,388
So here's the question,

302
00:16:32,107 --> 00:16:33,428
Li Shu is well aware of

303
00:16:34,668 --> 00:16:35,347
who wrote

304
00:16:35,508 --> 00:16:36,788
the anonymous letter,

305
00:16:36,867 --> 00:16:37,508
right?

306
00:16:38,107 --> 00:16:38,747
Then why did she

307
00:16:38,827 --> 00:16:40,068
frame you for it?

308
00:16:42,467 --> 00:16:43,148
Besides,

309
00:16:44,467 --> 00:16:45,428
most people at the institute

310
00:16:45,548 --> 00:16:46,467
likely know

311
00:16:46,548 --> 00:16:47,947
who wrote that anonymous letter.

312
00:16:48,428 --> 00:16:50,068
Gao Ping surely must know.

313
00:16:50,268 --> 00:16:51,347
If he knows,

314
00:16:52,308 --> 00:16:53,467
then why did he still

315
00:16:53,548 --> 00:16:54,707
dump the blame on you?

316
00:17:11,748 --> 00:17:12,427
Xiang Zhong,

317
00:17:12,867 --> 00:17:13,907
are you in Shanghai?

318
00:17:15,068 --> 00:17:15,788
Yes, I am.

319
00:17:17,028 --> 00:17:18,427
Come over and watch the kids for a bit.

320
00:17:19,347 --> 00:17:20,187
What's up?

321
00:17:20,907 --> 00:17:22,147
I need to rush out.

322
00:17:34,068 --> 00:17:34,708
Li Shu.

323
00:17:36,187 --> 00:17:36,827
Li Shu.

324
00:17:37,387 --> 00:17:38,308
Ms. Zhang.

325
00:17:43,427 --> 00:17:44,187
