332
00:17:57,308 --> 00:17:57,867
Alright.

333
00:17:58,508 --> 00:17:59,667
I'll let them know.

334
00:18:35,268 --> 00:18:36,788
(Xiang Qian: Li Shu, I know you're there.)

335
00:18:37,107 --> 00:18:38,468
(I need to talk to you.)

336
00:18:39,187 --> 00:18:40,907
(I'll wait for you at the café
across the street.)

337
00:18:41,427 --> 00:18:42,867
(No matter how late it is,
we need to meet.)

338
00:19:09,667 --> 00:19:10,228
Thank you.

339
00:19:13,548 --> 00:19:14,867
So you still insist

340
00:19:15,468 --> 00:19:16,548
that no one else

341
00:19:17,268 --> 00:19:17,988
besides you,

342
00:19:18,387 --> 00:19:19,308
your boyfriend,

343
00:19:19,788 --> 00:19:20,468
