353
00:19:45,827 --> 00:19:47,268
The car air freshener,

354
00:19:47,948 --> 00:19:48,948
the lipstick at home,

355
00:19:49,028 --> 00:19:50,028
your ultrasound report,

356
00:19:50,427 --> 00:19:51,187
you deliberately left them

357
00:19:51,228 --> 00:19:52,228
for me to see, right?

358
00:19:52,867 --> 00:19:53,827
To create a false impression

359
00:19:53,907 --> 00:19:54,867
of intimacy between you and Gao Ping,

360
00:19:55,028 --> 00:19:56,827
and to stir up conflict
between Gao Ping and me.

361
00:19:57,187 --> 00:19:57,708
Li Shu,

362
00:19:57,748 --> 00:19:59,347
you've already destroyed one family.

363
00:19:59,867 --> 00:20:01,387
Why do you still want

364
00:20:01,468 --> 00:20:02,907
to sabotage my relationship
with Gao Ping?

365
00:20:15,667 --> 00:20:16,587
Don't look at me like that.

366
00:20:17,068 --> 00:20:18,068
Go ask Gao Ping.

367
00:20:20,827 --> 00:20:21,748
Right now,

368
00:20:23,548 --> 00:20:24,387
I want to hear your explanation.

369
00:20:24,387 --> 00:20:25,627
I have nothing to explain.

370
00:20:26,308 --> 00:20:27,387
Li Shu, listen,

371
00:20:27,788 --> 00:20:28,988
asking you to meet me here

372
00:20:29,548 --> 00:20:30,587
is to give you

373
00:20:30,748 --> 00:20:32,068
a chance to explain yourself.

374
00:20:32,988 --> 00:20:34,907
I have certified recordings

375
00:20:35,548 --> 00:20:37,028
