376
00:20:37,028 --> 00:20:37,948
for defamation.

377
00:20:39,827 --> 00:20:40,948
Sue me?

378
00:20:41,548 --> 00:20:42,708
How amusing.

379
00:20:43,268 --> 00:20:45,028
Why don't you sue Gao Ping?

380
00:20:45,508 --> 00:20:47,387
He's the one who wants to divorce you.

381
00:20:51,788 --> 00:20:53,268
He's the one who wants to go abroad.

382
00:20:53,667 --> 00:20:55,508
He wants to go abroad alone.

383
00:20:56,667 --> 00:20:57,988
He doesn't want his whole family

384
00:20:58,068 --> 00:20:59,827
to be a burden to him.

385
00:21:06,387 --> 00:21:07,667
In truth, it's Gao Ping

386
00:21:07,708 --> 00:21:09,187
who's setting you up, isn't that right?

387
00:21:10,028 --> 00:21:11,627
He's the one who's responsible.

388
00:21:11,788 --> 00:21:13,107
You should confront him.

389
00:21:24,548 --> 00:21:25,948
And you're helping him

390
00:21:26,627 --> 00:21:27,708
by playing the mistress,

391
00:21:28,948 --> 00:21:29,587
making me suspicious,

392
00:21:29,627 --> 00:21:30,147
and leading me

393
00:21:30,187 --> 00:21:31,427
on a wild goose chase.

394
00:21:32,068 --> 00:21:33,427
How could you be so awful?

395
00:21:33,708 --> 00:21:34,748
You even came to my office,

396
00:21:34,867 --> 00:21:36,187
crying like a helpless victim,

397
00:21:36,827 --> 00:21:37,748
saying how difficult it was

398
00:21:37,788 --> 00:21:39,028
to get into the research institute.

399
00:21:39,508 --> 00:21:40,347
All you wanted was

400
00:21:40,427 --> 00:21:41,228
a chance to stay on

401
00:21:41,308 --> 00:21:42,107
as an assistant instructor.

402
00:21:42,187 --> 00:21:43,627
Someone like you as an instructor?

403
00:21:43,988 --> 00:21:44,667
What would you teach?

404
00:21:45,028 --> 00:21:46,587
How to be a homewrecker?

405
00:21:50,548 --> 00:21:51,708
What are you trying to get out of this?

406
00:21:53,867 --> 00:21:55,468
Can Gao Ping help you apply for a PhD?

407
00:21:56,028 --> 00:21:57,228
Or take you abroad?

408
00:21:57,627 --> 00:21:58,827
Or do you, Li Shu, just enjoy

409
00:21:58,827 --> 00:21:59,708
ruining other people's families

410
00:21:59,748 --> 00:22:00,667
and can't stand others' happiness?

411
00:22:00,708 --> 00:22:01,788
What I want is none of your business.

412
00:22:01,867 --> 00:22:02,548
Whether I like

413
00:22:02,548 --> 00:22:03,268
ruining others' families

414
00:22:03,308 --> 00:22:04,347
isn't your concern either.

415
00:22:04,468 --> 00:22:05,268
I just can't stand

416
00:22:05,347 --> 00:22:06,308
someone like you being happy.

417
00:22:06,508 --> 00:22:08,268
All I can say is, Gao Ping
and I are alike.

418
00:22:08,508 --> 00:22:09,347
Why can't we

419
00:22:09,347 --> 00:22:10,107
be pragmatic?

420
00:22:10,347 --> 00:22:11,147
Why can't we

421
00:22:11,187 --> 00:22:12,107
take the shortcut?

422
00:22:12,788 --> 00:22:14,187
We're just trying

423
00:22:14,268 --> 00:22:16,587
to create better opportunities
for ourselves.

424
00:22:18,587 --> 00:22:20,427
You're despicable.

425
00:22:23,988 --> 00:22:25,548
You have no conscience.

426
00:22:32,028 --> 00:22:33,068
Shortcuts

427
00:22:33,228 --> 00:22:34,587
