428
00:23:16,387 --> 00:23:17,308
Hello, Gao Ping?

429
00:23:18,587 --> 00:23:19,667
I need to talk

430
00:23:19,748 --> 00:23:21,068
to you urgently.

431
00:23:23,788 --> 00:23:24,948
Can we speak in person?

432
00:23:26,708 --> 00:23:27,827
Yes, right now.

433
00:23:29,748 --> 00:23:30,308
Alright,

434
00:23:30,347 --> 00:23:31,748
let's meet at the café downstairs.

435
00:23:34,587 --> 00:23:35,508
Alright, I'll be there.

436
00:23:50,548 --> 00:23:52,187
Going out this late?

437
00:23:53,107 --> 00:23:55,028
Yes, Mr. Lu suddenly

438
00:23:55,028 --> 00:23:56,228
