439
00:23:56,387 --> 00:23:57,187
I'm going out for a while.

440
00:23:58,627 --> 00:24:00,107
Come back soon.

441
00:24:00,468 --> 00:24:02,028
Okay, you get some sleep,

442
00:24:02,187 --> 00:24:02,748
baby.

443
00:24:09,788 --> 00:24:11,028
Drop me off

444
00:24:11,387 --> 00:24:12,028
at the entrance

445
00:24:12,068 --> 00:24:13,788
