447
00:24:18,308 --> 00:24:18,867
Yes, I'll be fine.

448
00:24:20,347 --> 00:24:21,827
I want to talk to him alone.

449
00:24:54,147 --> 00:24:54,827
Hello?

450
00:25:08,268 --> 00:25:09,627
