451
00:25:10,827 --> 00:25:11,508
Thanks.

452
00:25:42,788 --> 00:25:44,667
Not now, Jiang.

453
00:25:47,308 --> 00:25:49,427
I said not now.

454
00:25:52,347 --> 00:25:53,347
Are you an alien?

455
00:25:54,667 --> 00:25:56,107
I'm not in the mood.

456
00:25:57,107 --> 00:25:58,068
I don't want to, okay?

457
00:25:58,587 --> 00:25:59,187
No, Jiang.

458
00:25:59,187 --> 00:26:00,627
I said no.

459
00:26:01,107 --> 00:26:02,187
Get your hands off me.

460
00:26:05,748 --> 00:26:07,147
Must you reject me like this?

461
00:26:11,748 --> 00:26:12,587
I'll sleep downstairs.

462
00:27:04,867 --> 00:27:06,107
Gao Ping probably won't come.

463
00:27:06,667 --> 00:27:07,708
How do you know?

464
00:27:09,587 --> 00:27:10,708
I asked someone to check

465
00:27:10,748 --> 00:27:13,387
with his postdoctoral advisor, Mr. Lu.

466
00:27:14,827 --> 00:27:16,948
There was never a Fujian project.

467
00:27:20,627 --> 00:27:21,827
He's been deceiving you.

468
00:27:31,120 --> 00:27:35,560
(Your real-time position)

469
00:27:37,228 --> 00:27:37,867
He's here.

470
00:27:38,347 --> 00:27:39,308
His car is nearby.

471
00:28:08,387 --> 00:28:10,028
Have you been waiting by the roadside?

472
00:28:10,708 --> 00:28:11,308
Yes.

473
00:28:11,627 --> 00:28:12,748
Did you see

474
00:28:13,427 --> 00:28:14,107
when this car

475
00:28:14,187 --> 00:28:14,948
pulled in?

476
00:28:16,867 --> 00:28:18,147
Sorry, I was

477
00:28:18,508 --> 00:28:19,867
too focused on watching you.

478
00:28:26,667 --> 00:28:27,308
Sorry.

479
00:28:27,347 --> 00:28:29,107
The subscriber you have dialed
is powered off.

