00:29:16,988 --> 00:29:18,387
Don't worry too much.

494
00:29:18,907 --> 00:29:19,907
Just get a good night's sleep.

495
00:29:21,268 --> 00:29:22,468
I'll find him for you,

496
00:29:22,827 --> 00:29:23,948
and we'll ask him

497
00:29:24,387 --> 00:29:25,308
face-to-face.

498
00:29:26,028 --> 00:29:26,788
Thank you

499
00:29:27,068 --> 00:29:28,228
for staying with me so late.

500
00:29:28,907 --> 00:29:30,028
You should get some rest too.

501
00:29:30,508 --> 00:29:31,387
Get some sleep.

