536
00:32:15,107 --> 00:32:15,988
Who?

537
00:32:16,708 --> 00:32:17,387
Gao Ping.

538
00:32:18,308 --> 00:32:19,187
Gao Ping?

539
00:32:19,548 --> 00:32:20,347
