549
00:32:37,427 --> 00:32:38,028
Hurry.

550
00:32:39,068 --> 00:32:40,068
Got it.

551
00:32:40,427 --> 00:32:41,187
Thanks.

552
00:32:41,308 --> 00:32:41,907
Okay.

553
00:32:55,827 --> 00:32:56,667
