the manufacturing date.

556
00:32:59,508 --> 00:33:00,427
Did you bring your reading glasses?

557
00:33:00,587 --> 00:33:01,508
Yes, don't worry.

558
00:33:01,548 --> 00:33:02,228
I'll check carefully.

559
00:33:02,308 --> 00:33:02,907
That's right.

560
00:33:02,907 --> 00:33:03,867
Be sure to buy the fresh ones,

561
00:33:03,867 --> 00:33:04,867
not like the ones from yesterday.

562
00:33:04,948 --> 00:33:06,187
Ms. He.

563
00:33:06,427 --> 00:33:06,827
Miss.

564
00:33:07,068 --> 00:33:07,627
Get on it.

565
00:33:07,788 --> 00:33:08,308
Alright, I'm off.

566
00:33:08,468 --> 00:33:09,988
